org.apache.iceberg.transforms

Class Transforms

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.iceberg.transforms.Transforms

  • public class Transforms
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory methods for transforms.

    Most users should create transforms using a PartitionSpec.Builder#builderFor(Schema) partition spec builder}.

    See Also:
    The partition spec builder.
